@weswigham I think this class has to be `export`ed, or else there is no way to write this code:


```typescript
import multer from 'multer';

class Foo {
  multerFactory: ???;

  constructor() {
    this.multerFactory = multer({...});
  }  
}
```

Prior to this PR, we had `multer.Instance`, but this patch removes that from the exported namespace

